title: Love Where You Live! Senior Community 55+ ! APPLY TODAY
posting_body: ['****THE CHARLESTON**** PLANTATION AT QUAIL VALLEY', '2815 Cypress Point Dr, Missouri City, TX 77459', '$1,535/mo', 'CALL FOR YOUR PRIVATE TOUR', 'Plantation at Quail Valley is the premier senior living community with excellent amenities and beautiful apartment homes.', 'We offer the stress free lifestyle that senior adults long for and deserve.', 'Our apartment homes are stylish, bright and attractive.', 'Call for your personal tour and take in all', 'the amenities that are part of our community.', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage: 948 sq.ft.', 'Bedrooms: 2 Bedrooms', 'Bathrooms: 2 Baths', 'Parking:', 'Off Street Parking / Guest Parking', 'Lease Duration: 1 Year', 'Pets Policy: Cats & Dogs OK', 'Laundry: Connections In Unit', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'Clubhouse', 'Daily Activities', 'Transportation', 'Valet Trash Service', 'Gated Community', 'Courtesy Office on property', 'Elevators in all buildings', 'Housekeeping available', 'Off-street parking', 'CONTACT INFORMATION:', 'Sandra Holley', 'ParaWest Management', 'show contact info']
